def visit_FunctionDef(self, node):
    """ID: 30cf055e-4a70-446b-a016-640e286d3d5b"""
    self.name_stack.append(node.name)
    self.method_stack.append(node.name)
    for stmt in node.body:
        self.visit(stmt)
    self.method_stack.pop()
    self.name_stack.pop()
